text: Ragna Biskopstø Patawary (née Biskopstø; born 10 November 1980) is a Faroese footballer who plays as a defender for Klaksvíkar Ítróttarfelag. She has been a member of the Faroe Islands women's national team. ==References== Category:1980 births Category:Living people Category:Women's association football defenders Category:Faroese women's footballers Category:People from Klaksvík Category:Faroe Islands women's international footballers Category:Twin people from the Faroe Islands Category:Twin sportspeople
